Name: HellMaze
About the game: It's a game of cute characters' journey to find a cool drink in the wilderness desert. It is a game that can be enjoyed lightly only by keyboard operation. As you move through the maze, find coins and vending machines and pick up a cool beverage can from ice. Features - A maze puzzle arcade game that moves a 3D maze with 20 levels - 10 selectable characters with different stats - More than 30 traps and obstacles - More than 20 different mobs - Number of Challenges and Clear Time and Result Statistics - Show directions for beginners - Zoom out function for a wider view
